---
// Slide 18 · CTA Final — "Ligar a Máquina?" · fechamento
import SlideShell from '../SlideShell.astro'
---

<SlideShell
  variant="default"
  sbLeft="PRÓXIMO PASSO · DECIDIR"
  sbRight="// 19 / 19 · FECHAMENTO"
  navLeft="★ SISTEMA &gt; IMPROVISO · BORA PRA CIMA"
  navRight="@JOELBURIGO.COM.BR"
  navAcid={false}
>
  <div class="cta-radial"></div>

  <div class="cta-wrap">
    <div class="cta-kicker">// DECIDIR AGORA</div>
    <h1 class="cta-h1">
      LIGAR A<br />
      <span class="fire">MÁQUINA?</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="cta-sub">
      Você viu o sistema. Viu os cases. Viu o método.<br />
      Agora é só decidir qual caminho faz sentido <b>pra ti.</b>
    </p>

    <div class="cta-prices">
      <span class="cta-chip cta-chip-acid">★ VSS · R$ 1.997 À VISTA OU 12× R$ 166,42</span>
      <span class="cta-chip cta-chip-fire">★ ADVISORY · POR CONVITE</span>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-btns">
      <a href="/vendas-sem-segredos" class="cta-btn cta-btn-primary">
        VER VSS COMPLETO →
      </a>
      <a href="/advisory" class="cta-btn cta-btn-secondary">
        FALAR COM JOEL (ADVISORY) →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-foot">
      <div class="cta-foot-t">
        Daqui 90 dias você estará <b>90 dias mais perto</b> do sistema.<br />
        Ou <b>90 dias mais longe.</b> Escolhe.
      </div>
      <div class="cta-sign">
        ★ SISTEMA &gt; IMPROVISO · BORA PRA CIMA · LET'S GROW
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</SlideShell>

<style>
  .cta-radial {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 20%, rgba(198, 255, 0, 0.12), transparent 55%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-wrap {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 60px;
  }
  .cta-kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(12px, 1vw, 18px);
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    color: var(--jb-acid);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .cta-h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(72px, 11vw, 200px);
    line-height: 0.88;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--jb-cream);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .cta-h1 .fire { color: var(--jb-fire); }
  .cta-sub {
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 24px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--jb-fg-3);
    max-width: 1000px;
  }
  .cta-sub b { color: var(--jb-cream); }

  .cta-prices {
    margin-top: 32px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .cta-chip {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(11px, 1vw, 14px);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 1px solid;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .cta-chip-acid { color: var(--jb-acid); border-color: var(--jb-acid); }
  .cta-chip-fire { color: var(--jb-fire); border-color: var(--jb-fire); }

  .cta-btns {
    margin-top: 36px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .cta-btn {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(14px, 1.3vw, 20px);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 20px 32px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: transform var(--jb-dur) var(--jb-ease), box-shadow var(--jb-dur) var(--jb-ease);
  }
  .cta-btn-primary {
    background: var(--jb-fire);
    color: var(--jb-ink);
    box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 var(--jb-acid);
  }
  .cta-btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
    box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--jb-acid);
  }
  .cta-btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--jb-cream);
    border: 2px solid var(--jb-cream);
  }
  .cta-btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--jb-acid);
    color: var(--jb-acid);
  }

  .cta-foot {
    margin-top: 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .cta-foot-t {
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.1vw, 18px);
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--jb-fg-3);
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .cta-foot-t b { color: var(--jb-cream); }
  .cta-sign {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(11px, 0.9vw, 13px);
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    color: var(--jb-fg-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
</style>
